{"tid":1393942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"起義！起義！係起義呀！","createTime":"2019-08-01T09:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:06:42.000Z","uid":127735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"60624f4d9345c9995a8fb3fd8a1b571cb773e227","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"「起義」一詞有正面之意，中老一輩年輕既時候會比較成日聽到，有個「義」字係到比人感覺係做既正面既野。比起現代用既「抗爭」「抗命」甚至「革命」，中老一輩會覺得係一個「打仗」既概念，而佢地宜家食得住得安樂，又仲點會想打仗。<br />\n<br />\n我建議多用「起義」一詞黎繼續做文宣，番去以前19，20年代<br />\n<br />\n認同就推<br />\n唔認同就由佢沉"},{"pid":"db6af0ec0699975261e9ddbdeee05f48563bffbc","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:05:00.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"41c51f6b58db12a677efc1c0dd038bfbda19c296","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"04cdfcab6af0accf300255cefaa7bfb01bc72826","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:05:21.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"299cfea651e87b48bb4b7c5ce5a4f1470380369a","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"56612217b2181e2367758f8501cf2c6356b566bf","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"8c1f00aafd6b4aa0fa85f65aabee9652030bbe65","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:05:51.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"6f049a534d1788a893e20c38f30857900385cee2","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"b20b4d1e05b735c262a31d849c9af3ffc75112cd","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"23ad865effeeada410ce5d37925d794aa4bbf63d","tid":1393942,"uid":127735,"lik